  "title": "Call Centre Executive",
  "description": "<p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Novena<br />🕘 <strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday<br />💼 <strong>Salary:</strong> 2000-2400<br /></p><h3><strong>About the Role</strong></h3><p>We are looking for friendly and confident individuals to join our <strong>Call Centre team</strong>. This role focuses mainly on <strong>handling customer enquiries and outbound follow-ups</strong>, with opportunities to <strong>recommend suitable products or services</strong> where relevant.<br />Training will be provided, making this role suitable for <strong>entry-level candidates and fresh graduates</strong> who want to gain customer service.<br /></p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Handle inbound and outbound calls in a professional and friendly manner</p></li><li><p>Respond to customer enquiries and provide accurate information</p></li><li><p>Follow up with customers on applications, requests, or service matters</p></li><li><p>Recommend relevant products or services based on customer needs</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate customer records and call logs</p></li><li><p>Meet service standards <br /></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum GCE ‘N’ / ‘O’ Level, Diploma preferred</p></li><li><p>Entry-level candidates and fresh graduates welcome</p></li><li><p>Comfortable communicating over the phone</p></li><li><p>Customer-oriented with a positive attitude</p></li><li><p>Willingness to learn basic sales skills</p></li><li><p>Able to work in a fast-paced call center environment<br /></p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Comprehensive training provided</p></li><li><p>Supportive team environment</p></li><li><p>Career progression opportunities <br /></p><p>R25156061</p><p>Just Recruit Singapore Pte Ltd - EA12C6295</p></li></ul>",
